       const [editVesselPending, setEditVesselPending] = React.useState(false);
       ```
     - Added startEditVessel function to populate form with vessel data
     - Added saveEditVessel function to PATCH vessel via API
     - Added "Edit" button next to "Remove" button in vessel card header
     - Added inline edit form that appears when editingVesselId matches vessel:
